00:32:04,270 --> 00:32:05,550
Be careful.

592
00:32:05,550 --> 00:32:06,320
Are you okay?

593
00:32:07,030 --> 00:32:07,790
I'm fine.

594
00:32:07,790 --> 00:32:08,790
Take it easy.

595
00:32:16,550 --> 00:32:17,390
Be careful.

596
00:32:23,680 --> 00:32:26,450
[Meeting Room]

597
00:32:29,590 --> 00:32:31,120
Mr. Xiao, how can I help you?

598
00:32:31,270 --> 00:32:32,600
Let's talk in my office.

599
00:32:48,830 --> 00:32:49,750
Put it on for me.

600
00:32:50,910 --> 00:32:51,670
