609
00:33:34,550 --> 00:33:35,470
I can't do it.

610
00:33:35,470 --> 00:33:37,400
Let Chief Editor Chen do it for you.

611
00:33:39,030 --> 00:33:40,030
Are you jealous?

612
00:33:41,310 --> 00:33:43,240
