613
00:33:45,190 --> 00:33:46,150
Are you ready?

614
00:33:57,470 --> 00:33:58,720
Let me help you.

615
00:34:01,110 --> 00:34:02,110
Give it to Maomao.

616
00:34:05,990 --> 00:34:06,710
Okay.

617
00:34:13,870 --> 00:34:14,790
Assistant Mao.

618
00:34:15,429 --> 00:34:16,670
Help Mr. Xiao

619
00:34:16,670 --> 00:34:17,800
