626
00:34:27,190 --> 00:34:28,790
Do you know where he moved to?

627
00:34:29,790 --> 00:34:31,630
What's the matter?

628
00:34:32,590 --> 00:34:34,750
We need to film a home scene.

629
00:34:35,830 --> 00:34:37,389
He moved to Jialian.

630
00:34:37,389 --> 00:34:38,630
He's Xi's neighbor.

631
00:34:42,590 --> 00:34:43,650
Chief Editor Chen?

632
00:34:46,590 --> 00:34:47,750
Do you know

633
00:34:47,790 --> 00:34:49,469
if he will be home

634
00:34:49,469 --> 00:34:50,710
this Saturday morning?

635
00:34:50,710 --> 00:34:51,550
Let me take a look.

636
00:34:51,550 --> 00:34:52,110
Okay.

637
00:34:55,550 --> 00:34:56,469
He should be there.

638
00:34:56,469 --> 00:34:57,310
Do you need me

639
00:34:57,310 --> 00:34:58,470
to set a time with him?

640
00:34:58,470 --> 00:34:59,350
No, no.

641
00:34:59,350 --> 00:35:00,460
We want to do

642
00:35:00,460 --> 00:35:01,550
a surprise shoot.

643
00:35:01,630 --> 00:35:02,870
It's more realistic.

644
00:35:03,110 --> 00:35:04,030
Assistant Mao,

645
00:35:04,270 --> 00:35:05,870
you must keep it a secret for us.

646
00:35:05,870 --> 00:35:06,470
Okay.

647
00:35:06,710 --> 00:35:08,110
I'll get back to work now.

648
00:35:09,150 --> 00:35:09,870
Xiao,

649
00:35:11,070 --> 00:35:12,430
are we working overtime on Saturday?

650
00:35:12,430 --> 00:35:13,350
I'll arrange the recording

651
00:35:13,350 --> 00:35:14,460
and lighting staff.

652
00:35:14,460 --> 00:35:16,190
No, I'll go by myself.

653
00:35:16,190 --> 00:35:16,750
Okay.

654
00:35:42,230 --> 00:35:42,990
Yao.

655
00:35:43,670 --> 00:35:45,390
Yuyi wants to do teambuilding

656
00:35:45,390 --> 00:35:46,280
with our project team.

657
00:35:46,280 --> 00:35:47,310
Are you free?

658
00:35:47,950 --> 00:35:49,210
Is it arranged by them?

659
00:35:49,310 --> 00:35:50,110
Yes.

660
00:35:51,940 --> 00:35:52,710
I won't go.

661
00:36:22,470 --> 00:36:23,350
Lin Xi?

662
00:36:24,110 --> 00:36:25,310
Taking out the trash?

663
00:36:26,670 --> 00:36:27,910
What are you doing?

664
00:36:28,430 --> 00:36:29,630
Eating.

665
00:36:29,630 --> 00:36:31,270
