667
00:36:32,870 --> 00:36:33,830
I'll go now.

668
00:36:38,750 --> 00:36:41,270
Yicheng, it's me.

669
00:36:46,550 --> 00:36:48,010
Sorry to keep you waiting.

670
00:36:48,430 --> 00:36:49,430
What do you mean?

671
00:36:49,430 --> 00:36:50,360
Why are you here?

672
00:36:50,510 --> 00:36:51,870
We're supposed to shoot

673
00:36:51,870 --> 00:36:53,070
your home life today,

674
00:36:53,320 --> 00:36:54,150
but I only got a call

675
00:36:54,150 --> 00:36:55,430
from the cameraman when I entered the neighborhood

676
00:36:55,430 --> 00:36:58,160
that he couldn't come because something came up.

677
00:36:59,710 --> 00:37:01,920
This house is quite old.

678
00:37:03,270 --> 00:37:05,800
You probably can't rest well at night, right?

679
00:37:06,780 --> 00:37:08,860
Yicheng, if you need it,

680
00:37:08,860 --> 00:37:10,030
my friend has a large flat

681
00:37:10,030 --> 00:37:10,910
that they're renting out.

682
00:37:10,910 --> 00:37:11,550
No need.

683
00:37:13,550 --> 00:37:14,430
Right.

684
00:37:14,670 --> 00:37:16,470
The traffic is convenient here.

685
00:37:17,590 --> 00:37:19,190
Are you done looking around?

686
00:37:22,070 --> 00:37:23,800
Since we're not filming today,

687
00:37:24,910 --> 00:37:26,110
I won't hold you up.

688
00:37:28,750 --> 00:37:30,070
Old classmate,

689
00:37:30,630 --> 00:37:32,510
even if we don't talk about business,

690
00:37:32,510 --> 00:37:34,150
we can still catch up, right?

691
00:37:36,590 --> 00:37:37,670
Please.

692
00:37:37,670 --> 00:37:39,630
We've been classmates for ten years

693
00:37:39,630 --> 00:37:41,510
and we were in the same club.

694
00:37:41,790 --> 00:37:43,110
Is our friendship not enough

695
00:37:43,110 --> 00:37:45,370
for us to eat lunch and chat on a Saturday?

696
00:37:45,750 --> 00:37:46,470
Lin Xi,

697
00:37:48,750 --> 00:37:51,110
Chen Xiao wants to catch up with us.

698
00:37:51,830 --> 00:37:52,540
No need.

699
00:37:52,540 --> 00:37:53,670
We've known each other for so long.

700
00:37:53,670 --> 00:37:55,060
Is it not enough for us

701
00:37:55,060 --> 00:37:57,390
to catch up together on a Saturday? Right?

702
00:38:01,310 --> 00:38:02,150
Yes.

703
00:38:02,150 --> 00:38:03,390
It's been a long time.

704
00:38:03,390 --> 00:38:04,590
Let's do it together.

705
00:38:09,230 --> 00:38:10,070
All right.

706
00:38:10,110 --> 00:38:11,260
Let's eat.

707
00:38:15,750 --> 00:38:17,070
Yicheng,

708
00:38:18,070 --> 00:38:19,270
