709
00:38:23,790 --> 00:38:24,710
This is...

710
00:38:24,710 --> 00:38:25,790
I begged my mom for a long time

711
00:38:25,790 --> 00:38:27,390
before she agreed to make it.

712
00:38:29,550 --> 00:38:31,590
Did your mom cook all these dishes?

713
00:38:31,950 --> 00:38:32,750
Yes.

714
00:38:33,110 --> 00:38:33,910
You should know

715
00:38:33,910 --> 00:38:35,110
that my mom is a chairman.

716
00:38:35,110 --> 00:38:36,640
She hasn't cooked in years.

717
00:38:36,790 --> 00:38:37,830
Try it.

718
00:38:37,990 --> 00:38:39,920
She hasn't lost her skills, right?

719
00:38:40,710 --> 00:38:41,950
Thank her for me.

720
00:38:42,670 --> 00:38:44,630
My mom often tells me

721
00:38:44,630 --> 00:38:45,670
about the first time

722
00:38:45,670 --> 00:38:47,110
you came to my house.

723
00:38:47,430 --> 00:38:48,910
It was your first time eating drunken crab.

724
00:38:48,910 --> 00:38:50,110
You thought it was raw

725
00:38:50,190 --> 00:38:52,120
and insisted on getting it cooked.

726
00:38:55,430 --> 00:38:56,470
Look at me.

727
00:38:56,470 --> 00:38:57,870
Why do I keep talking about this?

728
00:38:57,870 --> 00:38:58,830
Lin Xi didn't know you

729
00:38:58,830 --> 00:38:59,870
at that time.

730
00:39:00,340 --> 00:39:01,270
It's okay.

731
00:39:02,390 --> 00:39:03,910
I remember

732
00:39:03,910 --> 00:39:05,970
you often came to my house for dinner.

733
00:39:07,230 --> 00:39:09,290
Zhou Shuang and Li Jun were there too.

734
00:39:12,270 --> 00:39:12,870
Here.

735
00:39:14,920 --> 00:39:16,710
Try this.

736
00:39:17,470 --> 00:39:18,600
This is appetizing.

737
00:39:21,350 --> 00:39:22,480
-Try it.
-Thank you.

738
00:39:28,190 --> 00:39:29,110
How is it?

739
00:39:35,310 --> 00:39:36,570
Were these intestines

740
00:39:36,790 --> 00:39:38,120
also cooked by your mom?

741
00:39:38,430 --> 00:39:39,750
No.

742
00:39:39,750 --> 00:39:41,470
This was by the owner of the small restaurant

743
00:39:41,470 --> 00:39:43,150
outside our school.

744
00:39:43,310 --> 00:39:44,350
Zhu?

745
00:39:44,710 --> 00:39:46,170
Did you have it before too?

746
00:39:48,670 --> 00:39:50,070
I did, occasionally.

747
00:39:50,550 --> 00:39:51,870
Occasionally,

748
00:39:51,870 --> 00:39:53,200
but you still remember?

749
00:39:53,750 --> 00:39:55,810
Their intestines are quite special.

750
00:39:58,200 --> 00:39:58,870
But isn't Zhu

751
00:39:58,870 --> 00:40:00,270
not here anymore?

752
00:40:00,350 --> 00:40:01,810
He came back a few days ago.

753
00:40:01,990 --> 00:40:03,120
By the way, Yicheng,

754
00:40:03,310 --> 00:40:04,510
Zhu invited us

755
00:40:04,510 --> 00:40:05,590
to have dinner together.

756
00:40:05,590 --> 00:40:07,590
He said he wanted to thank us

757
00:40:07,590 --> 00:40:08,980
for being his first customers back then.

758
00:40:08,980 --> 00:40:10,270
That time,

759
00:40:10,270 --> 00:40:11,670
our club went there together.

760
00:40:11,670 --> 00:40:13,190
There were more than ten people.

761
00:40:13,190 --> 00:40:14,910
It was the soft opening.

762
00:40:14,910 --> 00:40:16,280
Just the two of us went.

763
00:40:20,070 --> 00:40:21,530
Let me show you something.

764
00:40:27,430 --> 00:40:28,830
Zhu said it was this photo

765
00:40:28,830 --> 00:40:30,760
that inspired him.

766
00:40:31,030 --> 00:40:32,630
He said he wanted to build

767
00:40:32,630 --> 00:40:34,360
a lover wall in the restaurant.

768
00:40:34,550 --> 00:40:36,080
Do you remember this photo?

769
00:40:38,030 --> 00:40:39,290
I have something to do.

770
00:40:39,310 --> 00:40:40,270
You guys eat first.

771
00:40:40,270 --> 00:40:41,870
I won't disturb you anymore.

772
00:40:49,550 --> 00:40:50,790
Why did you say all of that

773
00:40:50,790 --> 00:40:51,670
in front of her?

774
00:40:53,830 --> 00:40:55,150
Weren't we catching up?

775
00:40:55,150 --> 00:40:57,010
You did it on purpose, didn't you?

776
00:40:57,670 --> 00:41:00,330
What are you talking about? I don't understand.

777
00:41:00,750 --> 00:41:01,750
You know that

778
00:41:01,750 --> 00:41:02,990
I still have feelings for Lin Xi.

779
00:41:02,990 --> 00:41:04,430
You said this on purpose

780
00:41:04,430 --> 00:41:05,910
to separate us, right?

781
00:41:36,390 --> 00:41:37,990
Chen Xiao, let me tell you.

782
00:41:38,420 --> 00:41:39,150
I hope

783
00:41:39,150 --> 00:41:40,390
you can understand one thing.

784
00:41:40,390 --> 00:41:42,710
Even if I don't get back together with her,

785
00:41:42,710 --> 00:41:44,150
it's impossible for us.

786
00:41:49,550 --> 00:41:50,950
Am I

787
00:41:52,310 --> 00:41:53,630
that bad in your eyes?

788
00:41:56,350 --> 00:41:57,270
No.

789
00:41:57,630 --> 00:41:59,710
But you just don't like me.

790
00:42:02,550 --> 00:42:03,350
Chen Xiao,

791
00:42:04,830 --> 00:42:05,790
loving someone

792
00:42:05,790 --> 00:42:08,050
isn't just about loving their good side.

793
00:42:08,350 --> 00:42:09,550
On the contrary,

794
00:42:09,790 --> 00:42:10,430
when you love someone,

795
00:42:10,430 --> 00:42:12,960
you may fall in love with their shortcomings.

796
00:42:13,310 --> 00:42:14,510
In your eyes,

797
00:42:15,430 --> 00:42:17,110
Lin Xi is someone who will

798
00:42:17,110 --> 00:42:18,510
do anything for her goal,

799
00:42:19,110 --> 00:42:20,470
but in my eyes,

800
00:42:20,470 --> 00:42:23,270
she's very brave and moving.

801
00:42:29,030 --> 00:42:30,110
Xiao Yicheng,

802
00:42:32,430 --> 00:42:34,790
would we have ended up together

803
00:42:35,590 --> 00:42:37,120
if I'd taken the initiative

804
00:42:38,390 --> 00:42:39,850
and been braver back then?

805
00:42:40,750 --> 00:42:41,950
How do you think

806
00:42:41,950 --> 00:42:44,480
I should answer this hypothetical question?

807
00:42:44,790 --> 00:42:46,390
But I only know

808
00:42:46,390 --> 00:42:48,070
that if I'm braver

809
00:42:48,070 --> 00:42:48,670
and take the initiative now,

810
00:42:48,670 --> 00:42:50,150
I can get her back.

811
00:42:50,430 --> 00:42:51,470
Understand?

812
00:43:17,950 --> 00:43:20,150
[Tong Xin]

813
00:43:18,790 --> 00:43:19,910
Call me back.

814
00:43:30,070 --> 00:43:30,710
Hello.

815
00:43:31,510 --> 00:43:33,950
Mr. Xiao, you finally picked up the phone.

816
00:43:34,750 --> 00:43:35,670
Sorry.

817
00:43:35,670 --> 00:43:36,920
I was busy just now.

818
00:43:38,230 --> 00:43:39,870
I've checked the team building agenda.

819
00:43:39,870 --> 00:43:40,910
There are no problems.

820
00:43:40,910 --> 00:43:41,710
Xiao,

821
00:43:41,710 --> 00:43:42,980
what if...

822
00:43:44,630 --> 00:43:47,290
What if Lin Xi doesn't appreciate your efforts?

823
00:43:51,840 --> 00:43:53,370
There are two types of love:

824
00:43:54,870 --> 00:43:56,200
childhood sweethearts

825
00:43:56,550 --> 00:43:57,950
and happily ever afters.

826
00:43:59,790 --> 00:44:00,950
Lin Xi

827
00:44:01,870 --> 00:44:03,990
is everything I know about love.

828
00:44:04,990 --> 00:44:07,510
Xiao, you will succeed.

829
00:44:08,030 --> 00:44:08,910
Thank you.

830
00:44:39,110 --> 00:44:40,150
Mom,

831
00:44:40,390 --> 00:44:42,070
