00:45:23,110 --> 00:45:25,510
Bruciare l'olio di mezzanotte.

857
00:45:26,950 --> 00:45:27,430
All right.

858
00:45:27,430 --> 00:45:28,280
You can

859
00:45:28,280 --> 00:45:29,390
read it with me.

860
00:45:29,390 --> 00:45:30,030
Bruciare l'olio di mezzanotte.

